        <num>CCP 924</num>
        <heading>924.  Form of exceptions</heading>
        <content>
          <p>Art. 924.  Form of exceptions
All exceptions shall comply with Articles 853, 854, and 863, and, whenever applicable, with Articles 855 through 861.  They shall set forth the name and surname of the exceptor, shall state with particularity the objections urged and the grounds thereof, and shall contain a prayer for the relief sought.</p>
        </content>
